{"search_data": "HaryanaHaryana Labour Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana \u2013 Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme Labor Dept. invites Haryana Labour Welfare Fund Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme (Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana) for labourers 2019 online application form at hrylabour.gov.in, registered labourers to get financial assistance equal to their minimum wages fixed by Haryana govt. if laborer suffers from any accident or any disease & got treatment by admitting in hospitals for 4 to 30 days in govt. / govt. empanelled hospitals, check application process, eligibility, conditions and complete details \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Table of Contents  Haryana Labour Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana 2019Haryana Labour Welfare Fund Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme Form OnlineHaryana Labour Welfare Board Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme EligibilityHaryana Labour Department Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana ConditionsHaryana Labour Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana 2019Haryana Labour Welfare Fund Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme 2019 aims to provide assistance to labourers in case they suffers from any accident or any other major ailment. This Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana by Haryana Labour Department will enable labourers to get their minimum wages in case they got admitted in the govt. / govt. aided hospitals.Haryana Labour Welfare Fund Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme Form OnlineAll the candidates can firstly visit the official website at hrylabour.gov.in. At the homepage, go to the \u201cE-Services\u201d section and make registration using Aadhaar card. Then make a login at the homepage of the official Labour dept. website and fill the Haryana Labour Welfare Fund Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme for labourers online registration form.To read the complete Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana details, click at the link \u2013 Haryana Labour Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana.Haryana Labour Welfare Board Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme EligibilityUnder the \u091a\u093f\u0915\u093f\u0924\u094d\u0938\u093e \u0938\u0939\u093e\u092f\u0924\u093e \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e of Haryana Labour Welfare Board, labour dept. provide minimum wages to the laborers admitted in hospitals suffering from accident / major disease. These wages would be given when the laborer got admitted in govt. / govt. aided hospitals for 4 to 30 days duration. The rates of wages would be same as those fixed as minimum wages by the Haryana government under Haryana Labour Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme. To avail the assistance, candidates must fulfill the eligibility criteria as shown below:-Eligibility / \u092a\u093e\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093eMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u09371Apply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093e1Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fAllContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940NoHaryana Labour Department Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana ConditionsAll the registered labourers must have minimum 1 years of membership / subscription.In the identity certificate of the registered labourers, date of application and subscription amount needs to be mentioned.All the laborers must be admitted for treatment in govt. / govt. aided hospitals for minimum 4 days to maximum 30 days. For this, they must produce a hospital certificate or proof.This facility is not applicable for medical treatment of more than 1 month in a single year."}